	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">An Interview with Leon Pryor </div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Kevin "Nocte" Dolley</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Aug 22, 2005, 11:48</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=An%20Interview%20with%20Leon%20Pryor%20&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Finterviews%2Farticle_5.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
